    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The title of Richard L. Berke's article, "Time Bomb in the White House" (June 6), was right on target. Can we really afford this new-age brand of kamikaze politics?</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>The title of Richard L. Berke's article, "Time Bomb in the White House" (June 6), was right on target. Can we really afford this new-age brand of kamikaze politics?</p>
        <p>If I worked in the White House as an associate director of personnel, do you think they'd let me use my job as a soapbox for my Judeo-Christian beliefs? SUZANNE MALONEY Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
